description: This top 10% Chukcha purrs with a rating of 48, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 144, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 3 for East, 5 for South, and 3 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
